text: Rudolf Vrána (14 July 1910 - 27 February 1983) was a Czech skier. He competed in the Nordic combined event at the 1936 Winter Olympics. ==References== Category:1910 births Category:1983 deaths Category:Czech male Nordic combined skiers Category:Olympic Nordic combined skiers of Czechoslovakia Category:Nordic combined skiers at the 1936 Winter Olympics Category:Place of birth missing
